
DEUS, qui nos hodiérna die Exaltatiónis sanctæ Crucis annua solemnitáte lætíficas: præsta, quæsumus; ut, cujus mystérium in terra cognóvimus, ejus redemptiónis præmia in cælo mereámur. Per eúmdem Dóminum.
O GOD, who dost gladden us this day with the yearly solemnity of the Exaltation of the holy Cross; grant, we beseech thee, that as we have learnt to know its mystery on earth, so we may merit to enjoy in heaven the reward of its redemption. Through the same.
